<Link id="l01169" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1169"><span class="doxyHighlight">    &#125; </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (SplatValue.<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apint/#a87d50d10274efe9688166584391ae489">isSignedIntN</a>(64)) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01170" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1170"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// If we have a 64 bit Splat value, we perform a similar sequence to the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01171" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1171"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// above:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01172" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1172"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01173" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1173"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// MIPS32:                            MIPS64:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01174" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1174"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   lui $res, %highest(val)            lui $res, %highest(val)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01175" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1175"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ori $res, $res, %higher(val)       ori $res, $res, %higher(val)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01176" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1176"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   lui $res2, %hi(val)                lui $res2, %hi(val)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01177" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1177"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ori $res2, %res2, %lo(val)         ori $res2, %res2, %lo(val)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01178" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1178"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   $res3 = fill $res2                 dinsu $res, $res2, 0, 32</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01179" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1179"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   $res4 = insert.w $res3&#91;1&#93;, $res    fill.d $res</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01180" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1180"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   splat.d $res4, 0</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01181" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1181"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01182" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1182"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The ability to use dinsu is guaranteed as MSA requires MIPSR5.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01183" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1183"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// This saves having to materialize the value by shifts and ors.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01184" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1184"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01185" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1185"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// FIXME: Implement the preferred sequence for MIPS64R6:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01186" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1186"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01187" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1187"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// MIPS64R6:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01188" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1188"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ori $res, $zero, %lo(val)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01189" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1189"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   daui $res, $res, %hi(val)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01190" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1190"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   dahi $res, $res, %higher(val)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01191" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1191"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   dati $res, $res, %highest(cal)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01192" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1192"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   fill.d $res</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01193" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1193"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01194" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1194"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01195" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1195"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a9ac8e4e13ad96a39c3f8db9ed633ad2baff50b4aa1c9cc2197ef898436641c911">Lo</a> = SplatValue.<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apint/#a0fa9845f80fa0642b31c238f4ab0d5ef">getLoBits</a>(16).<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apint/#a217e0207d9cc8e046c2dccbf0e4bb198">getZExtValue</a>();</span></CodeLine>
